{"tid":1513573,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一位發夢既前線既建議","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:49:28.000Z","uid":313187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d651b5fdabe131bb066c26851b87febdd39f5052","tid":1513573,"uid":313187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"經過多日既發夢 我同我果隊既隊友發現左發夢既時候 發生既問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">心態</span></strong><br />\n打敗你既對手 一定起心態上做起<br />\n唔可以覺得對方既玩具強大就驚<br />\n唔可以心態上強化對方<br />\n而係要搵解決方法<br />\n我現場見到偽勇武好多都有齊玩具<br />\n但係一射tg就跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住個個都跑走<br />\n得返d真勇武係到單打獨鬥<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">玩具</span></strong><br />\n我見好多人得3200同3m眼罩就上<br />\n喂 大佬 心態上唔驚姐 頂到先得下話<br />\n所以 有齊野先上啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">團隊</span></strong><br />\n唔該 搵隊友 話就話唔捉鬼姐<br />\n你都要保護自己啦 <br />\n最好有10個隊友啦<br />\n<br />\n走後退果陣唔該拉前面既人書包<br />\n唔好調轉跑走<br />\n唔係就冇得反擊啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下方唔該ching補充 利申:中學生"},{"pid":"59be103f39665dccb7bff390ad1a1e7118ad7f1b","tid":1513573,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Dk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=84a08